node.title: Police investigate death of two-year-old in Hamilton
node.description: Officers were flagged down in Heaphy Terrace about 11am on Saturday by the occupants of a vehicle who requested assistance with the girl.
node.content:
["Police are investigating the death of a two-year-old girl who was found unresponsive in a car in Hamilton.", "Officers were flagged down in Heaphy Terrace about 11am on Saturday by the occupants of a vehicle who requested assistance with the girl.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "She was taken to hospital where she died that evening.", "The death is being treated as unexplained.", "A scene examination has been completed at the child's home address and a post-mortem will be done today.", "Police said they were speaking with a number of people in relation to the death."]
